                <h2>Additional Aspects to Consider</h2>
                <hr class="brief--hr">



                <p>
                    In the brief description of a product design project, it's important to consider the following aspects:
                </p>

                <ul>
                    <li><strong>Budget:</strong> Define the project budget and financial constraints.</li>
